NAME
  autocraft - script for craft requesting.

SYNOPSIS
  autocraft
  autocraft [ITEM]
  autocraft [ITEM] [AMOUNT]

DESCRIPTION
  If no parameters are passed - prints list of available crafts.
  If ITEM parameter is passed - crafts ITEM with recipe one time.
  If ITEM and AMOUNT parameters are passed - crafts at least AMOUNT
of ITEM.
  Shows warning if craft was cancelled

EXAMPLES
  assuming, planks craft present
[In 1]> # autocraft
[Out 1]> 1   planks

[In 2]> # autocraft 1
[Out 2]> done

  this will craft planks 6 times (like at least 21)
[In 3]> # autocraft 1 21
[Out 3]> done